name: Marv Woodstrup Tennis Courts
description: Come play pickleball at Marv Woodstrup Tennis Courts in Red Bluff, CA! There are 4 outdoor asphalt courts. The lines are permanent, but you'll need to bring your own net. The courts are free. Amenities include lights.

name: Northside Park
description: Northside Park is a place to play pickleball in Corning, CA. There are 4 outdoor hard courts. These are dedicated courts with permanent lines and nets. The courts are free.

name: Tehama Family Fitness Center
description: Come play pickleball at Tehama Family Fitness Center in Red Bluff, CA! There are 3 indoor concrete courts. The lines are permanent, but you'll need to bring your own net. A one-time fee is required to play. The facility includes amenities like food, restrooms, and water.
